Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:44.03,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(275.2,385.601)}在\N天\N鵝\N湖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長 趕快想點辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.35,0:03:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點把小心音交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.92,0:03:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒有創聲部的節目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「白箱」不就只是個普通咖啡廳而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.02,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs45\frz-2\pos(627.2,502.399)}禁止對演員進行拍攝\N謝謝合作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 翼人還沒好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傷腦筋了 大家都在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就過了開演時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.13,0:04:07.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和傳聞中一樣 果然是個大帥哥呢 空筱翼人君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您過獎了 才沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.17,0:04:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣也就能理解 你為什麼那麼受女性歡迎了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.95,0:04:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每個月都能收到好幾十封粉絲來信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.35,0:04:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把身為議員的我晾在一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是寄給身為秘書的他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:21.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真實太讓人嫉妒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了 不過我們也得繼續努力才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25\an9}今天有急事去不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25\an9}我應該提前和你說過才對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.19,0:04:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25\an9}部長你起碼也要管理好大家的行程表才可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 我們在這裡相遇 果然就是命運啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.56,0:04:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像Destiny on the 阿佐谷？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 好土
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 竟然說阿佐谷就是命運之地什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.61,0:04:41.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿佐谷有什麼不好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說 涉谷什麼的 新宿什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種地方不是天天都會發生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裡太老套了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.11,0:04:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是說到在阿佐谷的命運般的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這多有意外性啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連自己都會嚇一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如self-surprise一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說 你手機從剛才開始就一直在響
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事啦 沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:05:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是關乎宇宙存亡的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.49,0:05:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須是宇宙的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻才最重要！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.21,0:05:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just now！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:15.79,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz9\pos(570,600)}對不起 請再稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘 你是不是有什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.38,0:05:22.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我也沒關係哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…非常…的重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 把…老婆婆…送送送…車車站
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆婆您想去車站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點距離沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.46,0:05:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻子店長也能理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的奶奶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到你的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.72,0:06:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要聽到求救的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論何時我都會出手相救的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要問為什麼的話 因為我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來是個不錯的小伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是被曬出問題了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.90,0:07:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡情愉悅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.19,0:07:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我就將你解放
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卷！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:55.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an7}你有什麼想要的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\an9}買了Racross第五卷送我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 什麼 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被NESTA病毒所感染 從而獸化的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}果然還是德國聯賽最精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.83,0:08:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}那本書的下卷 我不是已經借給你了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先它的實體會開始動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35\an8}在宮澤賢治的故鄉花卷裡提到的國內的詩人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.64,0:08:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後接下來將會發生的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.37,0:08:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 我今天先失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 喂 空筱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意義的侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伴隨著獸化的活性化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.26,0:08:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文字的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:34.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的概念將會開始暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全無法置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:41.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不卷的冰淇淋 超好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 是不是有點吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 會死人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.63,0:08:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.32,0:08:55.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.90,0:08:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土聞 你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那是小心音的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心音？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「白箱」的心音姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候不小心碰到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手製的嗎 必須還給她才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是給孫子買的禮物 但沒想到會這麼重
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是沒有你的話 我真不知道該怎麼辦好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:26.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 快看那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:42.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,龍捲風
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:50.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要動 我現在幫你剪開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是文字怪獸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.26,0:09:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真醜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.81,0:10:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前應該提醒過你了 不許在駕駛艙裡吃東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.71,0:10:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉 舞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個時刻終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.63,0:10:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要完成我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:26.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:27.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.84,0:10:34.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:37.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須快點去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放開我 我必須得去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.61,0:10:46.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不世 世界會……
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來…晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太慢了 小心音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.05,0:10:59.05,post - Copy,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(756,97)}今天臨時停業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:10:59.05,post - Copy,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(479,430)}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.31,0:11:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時停業
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在開始 本店臨時停業
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 真的非常抱歉 關門啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.32,0:11:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臨時停業是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼人君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.74,0:11:16.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是店長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在開始 要叫我司令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.47,0:11:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deava系統 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,系統連接完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.37,0:11:53.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vector Machine
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各機出擊準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向陣型Delta發佈指令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空筱 土聞兩位做好出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:11:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.76,0:12:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上來就實戰了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.54,0:12:08.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說這是第一次乘上真正的Vector吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們至今為止就是為了此時此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才努力磨練創聲力的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能讓Vector活動起來的 不是技術也不是知識
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是創聲力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用聲音喊出心聲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vector就會回應你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vector Outlane連結系統啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.29,0:12:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連結完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之 船到橋頭自然直啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地下儲水槽閥門開放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.48,0:12:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儲水桶開始進行流入作業
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,車站前的環形交叉路將暫時封鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻影屏障展開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.76,0:13:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,視域掩蓋運行一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起飛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土聞 空筱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.83,0:13:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 這傢伙就是這場騷亂的元兇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.88,0:13:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會在這裡 肯特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綺聲神 是你的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 額 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.31,0:14:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙就是世界的威脅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就由我來打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也讓我乘上那個機器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.74,0:14:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能會讓你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.44,0:14:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用這雙手去拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我就是救世主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好中二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:26.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 現在沒工夫和你瞎扯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.83,0:14:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全不管用啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.05,0:14:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用創聲力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是唯一可以對抗文字怪獸的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努蟲 用合體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.16,0:14:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合體的話 第一次真的很想和小心音合體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:57.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.91,0:14:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總比死這裡強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:14:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.34,0:15:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要保護這個怪獸就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.31,0:15:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝利條件也太簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要掉以輕心 總
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的 舞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:22.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了莊嚴大人崇高的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.47,0:15:23.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要驅逐一切 會妨礙到他的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就如舞亞所說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是司令說過的敵人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:32.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就預想到會有人妨礙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從我這裡奪走Vector Machine的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,粗朵櫻子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.98,0:15:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點吧 在你們重要的文字消失之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我也出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.92,0:16:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啟動吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Vector
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.04,0:16:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了一架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,綺聲神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是世界的威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什！為什麼那個孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:44.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼他能駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也擁有創聲力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 沒有穿著戰鬥服 也沒有經過正規訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能操縱Vector
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vector一號機 反應消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加緊進行空筱機和土聞機的回收
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣我就完成了使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.45,0:17:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我活著的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這邊已經沒有可以使用的機體了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.51,0:17:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首都高速以及主要幹道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止通行區域正在擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前為止還沒有出現死者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為積雨雲的異常現象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤道附近同時放生了三起……
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
